  <poweredBy>
    <!--
      Note: the "img" attribute doesn't work with 3.0 or 3.0-beta-3 because of MSITE-600
      The site.vm template in the Kuali skin has been edited to always print the
      Kuali Foundation logo and ignore the "img" attribute from site.xml.
      If a project wants to replace the Kuali Foundation logo with a project
      specific logo we will have to wait until maven-site-plugin 3.1 is released (or fix MSITE-600 ourselves)
      Once the maven-site-plugin is able to correctly deal with the "img" attribute again,
      edit site.vm in the maven-kuali-skin project to re-enable project specific
      logos
    -->
    <logo name="The Kuali Foundation &amp;reg" href="http://www.kuali.org/" />
  </poweredBy>
