    </head>

    <!-- Not working correctly. Child pom's assume that the link back to the parent pom is
      exactly one directory above them. /maven/plugins/xyz-plugin/0.0.1/index.html attempts to link back to
      /maven/kuali/76/index.html instead of /kuali/76/index.html
      <menu ref="parent" inherit="top" />
